- Predictions removed for iOS 8. For better typing please download SwiftKey Keyboard at www.appstore.com/SwiftKeyKeyboard

Now with landscape mode!

Thanks to helpful user feedback, this update has some special new features.

You can now:
- Use SwiftKey Note in landscape mode

If you have any further suggestions, ideas or bug reports, please reach us via the Support menu in settings

itunesNotes.standard: Take notes faster than ever with this innovative app that can predict your next words and phrases before you type them. While SwiftKey Note’s time-saving technology is evident right from the get-go, with extended use it can improve its accuracy by learning your writing style and which words you favor. Plus, with a slew of formatting options, built-in Evernote support, and useful ways to group your writing, your note-taking stays efficient and fast.

description.standard:
* THIS IS NOT SWIFTKEY KEYBOARD 
- please search for 'SwiftKey Keyboard' for faster, easier typing across all the apps on your iPhone, iPad or iPod touch.

Note is a beautiful, streamlined note-taking app with a powerful keyboard, giving users the fastest way to take notes on an iPhone and iPad. Using magical prediction technology, it intelligently autocorrects words as you type and offers next-word predictions based on the unique way you use words together. It gets smarter the more you use it, and adapts with you over time. A quick and intuitive notebook to store and share your thoughts, Note lets you take notes as you think in a faster and more powerful way. 

TAILORED TO YOU 
Note learns from you to offer personalized predictions. It understands the context of what you’re typing and can quickly learn the words and phrases that matter to you as you take notes. 

EVERNOTE® SYNC 
Connect with Evernote to teach Note’s autocorrect how you write based on your archive and enable instant backup of all your notes to the Evernote platform. Never lose a note again and keep your content consistent across all of your devices. 

EASY TAGGING AND FORMATTING 
Tag your notes and group related notes together in Notebooks for super-fast retrieval. Flexible organization allows you to create, edit and delete a Notebook and/or Tag.

MULTILINGUAL TYPING 
Use up to three languages at a time for accurate multilingual autocorrect and word suggestions. Note supports typing in English, Spanish, French, German and Italian.  

AWARD-WINNING TECHNOLOGY 
SwiftKey’s smart prediction technology is loved and trusted by millions. The company has been recognized as among the Top 10 Most Innovative Mobile Companies in the World by Fast Company and the No 1 Hottest Startup in London by Wired Magazine. 

NOTE INCLUDES: 
Organize your thoughts: group related notes together in Notebooks; 
Label and categorize your notes with tags for easy searching; 
Share your notes with other apps using Facebook, Twitter, AirDrop, Messages, Mail or Copy To Clipboard; 
Track your stats: get up-to-date analysis of your productivity including Efficiency, Keystrokes Saved, Typos Corrected, Words Predicted and Words Completed; 
Easy Tutorial: A fun and engaging tutorial introduces new users to SwiftKey prediction technology; 
Languages supported are: English (US), English (UK), Spanish (ES), Spanish (US), German, French (FR), French (CA), Italian; 
Support for portrait and landscape mode on iPad and iPhone for customizable note-taking experience. 

--- 
Supports iPhones, iPads and iPod touch devices running iOS 6 and above. Formatting and features from version 1.8 are not currently supported on iOS6 or in iOS 8.
